  "title": "TiledTileset",
  "description": "A parsed Tiled tileset — either embedded inline in a map's `tilesets` array, or parsed from an external `.tsj` file referenced by it. firstGid and lastGid define the inclusive range of global tile ids (after masking flip/rotation flags via `maskTiledGid`) that this tileset owns within its owning TiledMap.",
